Load EEG data from PhysioNet (CHB-MIT) eeg_path = "chb01_01.edf" try: if not os.path.exists(eeg_path): raise FileNotFoundError("chb01_01.edf not found in CNE_LFG") raw = mne.io.read_raw_edf(eeg_path, preload=True) eeg_data = raw.get_data(picks=[0])[0] # First channel (FP1-F7) eeg_data = detrend(eeg_data[:10000]) # First 10,000 samples (~40s at 256Hz) print("EEG data loaded: CHB-MIT, channel FP1-F7") except Exception as e: print(f"EEG load failed: {e}.
